Seals



Many seals were on the rocks very close to the viewing platform at the end of the boardwalk. Even with the long lens, I needed to crop, but not excessively.
Taken Monday, December 29, 2003, 12:47:38pm.  Original image size: 2560x2048, 6.5Mb
Technical details: Canon EOS D60, 1/80s @ F5.6, ISO 100, 70-200mm/F2.8+1.4x @ 280mm (448mm equiv)
